Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 01:06:55 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] ADD review-completion prompts so clean patch-agent
 reviews require yes/no closure

Clean review completion needs an explicit user decision before a patch-agent chat disappears from active work. The controller records yes/no acknowledgements without unnecessary backend resumes, reopens chats on follow-up, and suffixes repeated markers so each review cycle remains visible.
